Package: hpmicrosimr
Type: Package
Title: This package simulates the uptake of heat pumps and energy efficiency upgrades by Irish households.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joseph", "Wheatley", email = "joe.wheatley@ucd.ie", role = c("aut", "cre")),
